Temilayo Abodunrin (amụrụ na 19 Nọvemba 2009) bụ onye Naijirịa na-akpọ saxophon. A maara ya nke ọma maka nsụgharị Duduke na Jowo.
Temilayo Abodunrin si Offa na Kwara Steetị, etiti Naijirịa. O nwere ụmụnne nwoke abụọ na-akpọkwa ngwá egwu
Ọ gara Parara Music School mgbe ndị mụrụ ya chọpụtara banyere mmasị ya na egwu.

Temilayo Abodunrin malitere ịkpọ saxophone mgbe ọ dị afọ isii. Ọ na-eme ọtụtụ kọntaktị na ndị na-ese ihe na Naijirịa a ma ama dị ka Johnny Drille, Tope Alabi, Makayla Malaka, Wole Oni na ụfọdụ ndị ọzọ. Temilayo, kpakpando nwere ọtụtụ nkà emeela nke mbụ ya na ihe nkiri akpọrọ "The Weight" nke Tope Alabi dere
A maara Temilayo nke ọma maka mbipụta ya nke Duduke nke Simi na Jowo nke Davido nke nwetara nnabata zuru oke.

N'ajụjụ ọnụ ya na Nigeria Tribune, Temilayo nyochara na ọ malitere dị ka onye na-akpọ keyboard tupu ọ ghọọ onye na-akụ saxophon. N'ajụjụ ọnụ ahụ, o kwuru na ọ gara kọntaktị ebe a kpọrọ ya ka ọ kpọọ keyboard ma zute ụmụaka ndị ọzọ dị ka ya na-akpọ saxophone
O kwuru, ịnụ ụda mara mma mere ka ọ mụta saxophone
Ọ wepụtara egwu izizi ya akpọrọ AYO n'afọ 2020. Ọ sonyeere onye a họpụtara na Grammy Award Bankulli na onye na-emepụta egwu RotimiKeys
Ooni nke Ife cameo-ed na vidiyo egwu ahụ.
N'afọ 2019, a kpọrọ Temilayo Abodunrin ka ọ rụọ ọrụ na oge 11 nke Channels International Kids Cup.
Na 3 Jenụwarị 2021, ọ bụ akụkụ nke Ogo Yoruba Awards (O.Y.A) 2020.
